{
  "stem": "13096.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, they were in-- You go ahead, my sister say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And if you are alive, tell our brothers how we-- how we die.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "How we loved them and everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And say thank you for all the help they've given us while we were in Rhodes Island.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were sending, you know, money and parcels and all this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But that is the end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I can't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then, what I did, I sat next to my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I said to her, because I give her courage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Listen, if you sit it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I'm not standing either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "If you come out, I'll stand myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Otherwise, I will kill-- I will die with you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then, and then my sister, you know, she stand up for my sake.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "After a few kilometers, it was the other way around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But it was one another giving us courage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then we had-- we arrived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then we were walking and walking and walking during the night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Eventually, you know, it was-- all the time, the Germans on all the sides.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We were surrounded by Germans with guns in their hands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Eventually, comes, like you say a second time, a motorbike.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Now, you tell me if he's not God, this one, what it is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because what happened to us twice in the same period.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Come a motorbike and tell the Germans that they were, you know, with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "If they want to be alive, to-- to run for their lives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "The place where we're supposed to be taken to be-- you know, to be killed has already been occupied by the Germans-- by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They better run if they don't want to be killed, themselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So we didn't know what they spoke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We didn't know a thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
